# Walkthrough Descriptions
enchantment.sharpness.walkthrough = Increases melee damage by {amount}% per level. Applies to swords and axes.
enchantment.life_leech.walkthrough = Heals attacker for {amount}% of damage dealt. Applies to melee weapons.
enchantment.durability.walkthrough = Reduces durability loss chance by {amount}% per level. Applies to all weapons, tools, and armor.
enchantment.sturdy.walkthrough = Prevents max durability loss when repairing. Applies to all weapons, tools, and armor.
enchantment.dexterity.walkthrough = Reduces stamina costs by {amount}% per level. Applies to melee weapons, shields, and staffs.
enchantment.protection.walkthrough = Reduces incoming physical damage by {amount}% per armor piece per level. Applies to armor.
enchantment.efficiency.walkthrough = Increases mining speed by {amount}% per level. Applies to pickaxes, axes, and shovels.\n\nFor now this enchantment can only increase how fast a block breaks, not how fast your pickaxe swings due to Hytale limitations.
enchantment.fortune.walkthrough = Increases chance for extra ore/crystal drops by {amount}% per level. Applies to pickaxes. Not combinable with Pick Perfect or Smelting.
enchantment.smelting.walkthrough = Automatically smelts mined blocks. Applies to pickaxes. Not combinable with Pick Perfect or Fortune.
enchantment.strength.walkthrough = Increases projectile damage by {amount}% per level. Applies to ranged weapons.
enchantment.eagles_eye.walkthrough = Increases projectile damage by up to {amount}% based on distance per level. Applies to ranged weapons.
enchantment.looting.walkthrough = Increases mob max drop rates by {amount}% per level and boosts the chance of rare drops. Applies to melee weapons, ranged weapons, and staffs.
enchantment.feather_falling.walkthrough = Reduces fall damage by {amount}% per level. Applies to boots.
enchantment.waterbreathing.walkthrough = Reduces oxygen drain by {amount}% per level. Applies to helmets.
enchantment.burn.walkthrough = Sets target on fire, dealing {amount} damage per second for {duration} seconds, and lets it drop cooked variants of its drops. Applies to melee and ranged weapons. Not combinable with Freeze.
enchantment.freeze.walkthrough = Slows target by {amount}% for {duration} seconds on hit. Applies to melee and ranged weapons. Not combinable with Burn.
enchantment.eternal_shot.walkthrough = Lets you shoot arrows without consuming them. You still need 1 arrow in your inventory. Applies to ranged weapons.
enchantment.pick_perfect.walkthrough = Mined blocks drop themselves instead of their usual drops. Applies to pickaxes, axes, and shovels. Not combinable with Fortune or Smelting.
enchantment.thrift.walkthrough = Restores {amount}% of mana spent on hit per level. Applies to mana staffs.
enchantment.elemental_heart.walkthrough = Elemental Staffs do not consume essence when casting. Applies to essence staffs.
enchantment.knockback.walkthrough = Knocks targets back on hit. Applies to melee weapons.
enchantment.reflection.walkthrough = Reflects {amount}% of blocked damage back to the attacker per level. Applies to shields. Not combinable with Absorption.
enchantment.absorption.walkthrough = Heals blocker for {amount}% of blocked damage per level. Applies to shields. Not combinable with Reflection.
enchantment.fast_swim.walkthrough = Increases swim speed by {amount}% per level. Applies to gloves.
enchantment.night_vision.walkthrough = Enhances visibility in dark environments such as caves, nighttime, and underwater. Applies to helmets.\n\nThis enchantment is disabled by default as I am not quite pleased with the quality of the effect. But it's the best of what's possible with the current Hytale limitations.
enchantment.ranged_protection.walkthrough = Reduces incoming projectile and magic damage by {amount}% per armor piece per level. Applies to armor.
enchantment.frenzy.walkthrough = Increases signature charge rate by {amount}% per level. Applies to all weapons and staffs.
enchantment.riposte.walkthrough = This is a collab Enchantment with the Perfect Parries mod and will only work if both mods are installed.\n\nIncreases counter attack damage by {amount}% per level. Applies to melee weapons.
enchantment.coup_de_grace.walkthrough = This is a collab Enchantment with the Perfect Parries mod and will only work if both mods are installed.\n\nIncreases damage to stunned enemies by {amount}% per level. Applies to melee weapons.
enchantment.poison.walkthrough = Poisons targets on hit, dealing {amount} damage per second for {duration} seconds. Applies to melee and ranged weapons. Not combinable with Burn.
enchantment.environmental_protection.walkthrough = Reduces incoming elemental and environmental damage (fire, ice, cacti, and other hazards) by {amount}% per armor piece per level, and proportionally mitigates the slow intensity of the Freeze enchantment. Applies to armor.


